  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Apocalypse-scale Eldar novel set at the Battle of Duriel. Prince Yriel of Iyanden — carrying the consequences of an earlier engagement his farseers diverted into the warp — learns that the diverted fragment of Hive Fleet Kraken has re-emerged on a collision course with Hive Fleet Leviathan, and that the two swarms' genetic exchange would produce something the galaxy cannot survive. Yriel forges an uneasy three-way alliance with the Aspect-Warrior swordwind of Biel-Tan and the Dark Eldar of Commorragh, who fight only as long as the soul-toll suits them. Wraithguard, Aspect shrines, Kabal raiders and Tyranid bioforms collide across battlefield set pieces; a somber-cosmic register in which even victory only postpones the long extinction.",
